I would climb up at HP as a teenager and hang on to this machine and write programs for them.
How to Improve Innovation:
Several times in the interview, Jobs talks about how to spontaneously invent new products.
Early in his career, when he installed some circuit boards, he was asked by a customer to assemble the whole computer.
