"This is a good result, but it carries some risk as we have not scored an away goal," regrets Bento.
"We will compete against a team that has high technical qualities and has players with a lot of individual qualities," he added.
As in Zenica, the Portuguese would have in mind to put maximum pressure on the Bosnians right from the start, so as not to give them time to think.
A good idea, provided that it is put into action this time.
